## The Circle Ci will trigger many scripts:

## 1) Setting up (Node - AWS cli -Eb cli)

## 2) Getting ready for building/deployment:

- Setting up the environment variables
- preparing the desired version of nodejS
- Ensuring code is checked out
- install all the dependecies in the package.json [Front-end]
- install all the dependecies in the package.json [Back-end]
- initalizing the application to prepare the build folder for the [Front-end]
- initalizing the application to prepare the build folder for the [Back-end]
- Triggring the deployment of the whole application
